data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! COME SEE THIS GREAT FAMILY HOME W/ LARGE FENCED BACKYARD AND DECK! Welcome to your spacious oasis in Port Saint John! This exceptional home, with four bedrooms, two baths, and over 2000 square feet of living space, is a testament to pride of ownership. The generous family room invites gatherings and seamlessly connects to the inviting backyard area. Imagine lazy afternoons lounging on the expansive deck, taking in the view of your private, fenced yard - the perfect retreat. Modernized baths add a touch of luxury to your daily routine. With NO HOA restrictions there's plenty of room for all your toys!! Don't miss this Port Saint John GEM!! **Tax records do not reflect enclosed Florida Room & added 4th bedroom. Roof 2018, A/C 2017, Hot water heater 2022
